    dc:creator "Dankittipakul, Pakawin; Koh, Joseph K. H.; Singtripop, Tippawan" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Three new species and a new record of the spider genus Mallinella Strand, 1906 from Brunei (Araneae, Zodariidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225301>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225302>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225304> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225301>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. 1 – 3. Habitus. 1. Mallinella myrmecophaga sp. nov., female holotype. 2. M. platyrhyncha sp. nov., female holotype. 3. M. merimbunenis sp. nov., female paratype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225301/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225302>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 11. 4. Leg I – III, showing tubercle (indicated by arrow). 5 – 9, 11. Epigyne, ventral. 10. Internal female genitalia, anterior. 4. Mallinella merimbunenis sp. nov., male holotype. 5. M. bigemina Dankittipakul, Jocqué & Singtripop, 2012, new material from Brunei. 6. M. bigemina, female holotype. 7. M. albomaculata (Bosmans & Hillyard, 1990), female paratype. 8. M. merimbunenis sp. nov., female paratype. 9 – 10. M. myrmecophaga sp. nov., female holotype. 11. M. platyrhyncha sp. nov., female holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225302/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.225304>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 25. Mallinella myrmecophaga sp. nov., female holotype. 22. Internal female genitalia, dorsal. 24. Ditto, lateral. 23. Left spermatheca, anterior. 25. Right spermatheca, contralateral. Scale bar = 0.25 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225304/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

